milestones.description: John Davison and Ashish Bagai's 106-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 65 between Chumney and Qaiser Ali
Johnston and Eoin Morgan's 67-run partnership is IRE's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 48 between Andrew White and Niall O'Brien
Kevin O'Brien has become the top scorer for IRE in ODIs with 320 runs, going past Porterfield's 286
John Davison and Ashish Bagai's 106-run partnership is CAN's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 100 between Ashif Mulla and Ashish Bagai
Ashish Bagai has scored 2 hundreds in ODIs, the most for CAN breaking John Davison's record
Johnston has broken the record for most sixes (8) in ODIs for IRE, going past Kevin O'Brien's 7
Kevin O'Brien has scored 3 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for IRE breaking Porterfield's record
Cummins has conceded the most runs in an innings (74) in ODIs for CAN, going past Steven Welsh's record of 68
Andre Botha has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (7) for IRE, going past Johnston
